  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d85\u0db7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd\u0d9c\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith's challenge",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "If you have the ability to work with me, I challenge the cardboard heroes who are dressed for the presidency to do it, said the leader of the National United People's Party, Mr. Sajith Premadasa, in Dambulla.",
        "Samagi Jana Balawega's Dambulla Constituency Organizer U.R. Mr. Daya Nandasiri was addressing a public meeting in Dambulla and the leader of the opposition party Mr. Sajith Premadasa made this challenge. This was organized at Dambulla Nissanka ground.",
        "He said that the National Unity People's Force will achieve a great victory in a fair election.",
        "Individuals who claim to be bosses of each group and each individual are making suits for the presidency with great pleasure. They are asking those who sew suits whether they are capable of developing the country and whether they are capable of serving the people.",
        "If possible, come to serve the race to work with me and challenge the presidential dreamers. Not only that, he also said that he would invite."
      ],
